/F2 13 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 613.0 Tm (The recovery in three moves) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.0 596.0 Tm (1. Acknowledge genuinely: "That is fair, thanks for being direct.") Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 582.0 Tm (2. Ask one clarifying question to separate a reflex from a real no.) Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 568.0 Tm (3. If a door opens, offer one small next step; if not, thank them and end.) Tj
/F2 13 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 548.0 Tm (Questions that respect the person) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 66.0 531.0 Tm (- "Is it the timing, or is this just not something you deal with?") Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 517.0 Tm (- "Fair enough - out of interest, is it a priority thing or a fit thing?") Tj
1 0 0 1 66.0 503.0 Tm (- "Understood. Would it help if I checked back another time, or should I leave it?") Tj
