/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 466.0 Tm (Prospect: "Not interested." You: "That is fair, thanks for being direct. Can I ask - is) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 452.0 Tm (it that the timing is off, or that this kind of thing is not a priority right now?") Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 438.0 Tm (Prospect: "Just not a priority this quarter." You: "Understood. I will not chase you -) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 424.0 Tm (would a check-in next quarter be welcome, or would you rather I close this out?") Tj
