/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 56.0 383.0 Tm (One honest question after a "not interested" is fair; a second push after a clear,) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 369.0 Tm (repeated no is not. Never imply the prospect is making a mistake or use guilt to keep) Tj
1 0 0 1 56.0 355.0 Tm (them talking. A firm no is a complete answer - thank them and end the call.) Tj
